# 三、柱状图（Bar Chart）真正高分技巧

很多人：

# “按顺序念柱子”

这是6分写法。

真正高分：

# “分类 + 比较 + 趋势”

---

# 例如：

低分：

> A was 20.
> B was 30.
> C was 40.

这是读数据。

---

# 高分：

> Category C recorded the highest figure, whereas A remained the smallest group.

这是：

# 总结关系。

---

# 四、柱状图写作核心技巧（超级重要）

---

# 1. 不要按顺序念数据

❌：

2007...
2011...
2015...

这样容易流水账。

---

# 正确：

## 按：

* 最大值
* 最小值
* 增长最快
* 稳定类别

分类。

---

# 2. 一定要 comparison

IELTS Task1：

# 核心就是 compare。

---

# 高分句：

> X was considerably higher than Y.

> X exceeded Y by approximately ...

> In contrast, ...

---

# 3. 数据要“压缩”

不要：

> from 20 to 40

而是：

> doubled

不要：

> from 40 to 20

而是：

> halved

---

# 五、柱状图万能高级句式（必须会）

---

# 1. 最大最小

> X constituted the largest category.

> X recorded the highest figure.

> X remained the smallest group.

---

# 2. 稳定

> X remained relatively stable.

> X showed little overall change.

---

# 3. 上升

> X increased significantly.

> X experienced substantial growth.

> X rose sharply.

---

# 4. 下降

> X declined gradually.

> X experienced a downward trend.

> X fell considerably.

---

# 5. 对比

> By contrast, ...

> In comparison with ...

> Whereas X..., Y...

---

